{"tid":2041263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果：澳洲女子認企圖襲警囚三個月","createTime":"2020-05-29T06:29:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T07:07:13.000Z","uid":115273,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1fbe568fbddbd27f97d12c6464235b4f78498c82","tid":2041263,"uid":115273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:29:02.000Z","msg":"【蘋果日報】去年11月12日「破曉行動」三罷當日，澳洲籍女插畫師在中環行人天橋向下掟磚，協助示威者築路障，當時馬路上有一批警員正在推進。她早前在東區裁判法院承認企圖襲警罪。裁判官香淑嫻今斥責被告所作行為嚴重危害前線警務人員的安全，判她即時監禁三個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200529/GFYO25PHQ5WY7A7BUZKH2ASRKE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200529%2FGFYO25PHQ5WY7A7BUZKH2ASRKE%2F&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33C%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=50913759\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200529%2FGFYO25PHQ5WY7A7BUZKH2ASRKE%2F&h=cbda11b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200529/GFYO25PHQ5WY7A7BUZKH2ASRKE/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6133ad5e6aacb2d24d573987ad3c5b031fbdef4c","tid":2041263,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:45:08.000Z","msg":"真香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6e3922b7e3f940890aa6ee94c6e9b0ef0377c2","tid":2041263,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1925dc9f813fe464269b9ce4c0e598ad8353ad3f","tid":2041263,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:57:52.000Z","msg":"澳洲咁奶共 自己人食返"},{"pid":"ddbfc8a069f0893dfa238f2ae2344b2b1601ba36","tid":2041263,"uid":45087,"like":0,"dislike":